- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper deals with modeling rumor spreading in social networks.
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is also likely as the paper models the problem as a strategic game between two players.
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is relevant as the paper deals with network administration and estimation strategies.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with controlling the spread of rumors in a network.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is relevant as the paper deals with hiding the identity of the rumor source from the network administrator.
